end_position.description:
The end position of the mention.

Example message: &quot;@Shrijana How are you?&quot;
In this case, the end position of the mention &quot;@Shrijana&quot; is 8. Hence, the value of this field is 8.

start_position.description:
The start position of the mention(&quot;@&quot;) in the message string. 

For example if you want to include the mention at the beginning of the message, the value for this field is 0. 

Example message: &quot;@Shrijana How are you?&quot;

